\c 94
\s Jehovha ndiye Mutongi akarurama
\p
\v 1 Jehovha, Mwari mutsivi, imwi Mwari mutsivi, penyai.
\v 2 Zvisimudzei, imwi Mutongi wenyika; Ipai vanozvikudza sezvavakafanira.
\v 3 Jehovha, vakaipa vachafara kwazvo kusvikira rinhiko, Vakaipa vachafara kwazvo kusvikira rinhi?
\v 4 Vanongotaura havo, vanotaura vachizvikudza, Vaiti vese vezvakaipa vanoita manyawi.
\v 5 Vanopwanya vanhu venyu, Jehovha, Vachitambudza nhaka yenyu.
\v 6 Vanouraya chirikadzi nomweni, Nenherera vanodziuraya.
\v 7 Vachiti, Jehovha haazvioni, Mwari waJakove haazvirangariri.
\v 8 Rangarirai imwi vasina njere pakati pavanhu; nemwi mapenzi, muchava vakachenjera rinhiko?
\v 9 Iye, akasima nzeve, haanganzwi here? Iye, akaumba ziso, haangaoni here?
\v 10 Iye, anoranga vahedheni, haangarairi here? Iye, anodzidzisa vanhu zivo haazivi here?
\v 11 Jehovha anoziva kufunga kwavanhu,) Kuti hazvina maturo.
\v 12 Akaropafadzwa munhu, anorangwa nemi, Jehovha, lye wamunodzidzisa pamurairo wenyu;
\v 13 Kuti mumuzorodzei pamazuva okutambudzika, Kusvikira vakaipa vachererwa gomba.
\v 14 Nokuti Jehovha haangarasi  i vanhu vake, Uye haangasii nhaka yake.
\v 15 Nokuti kutonga kuchadzokera kukururama; Vese vane moyo yakarurama vachakutevera.
\v 16 Ndianiko achandirwira pavaiti vezvakaipa? Ndianiko achandibatsira panavanoita zvakaipa?
\v 17 Dai Jehovha aisava mubatsiri wangu, Mweya wangu ungadai wakakurumidza kugara pakati mwii.
\v 18 Panguva yandakati, Rutsoka rwangu rwotedzemuka. Tsitsi dzenyu,Jehovha, dzakanditsigira.
\v 19 Mundangariro dzangu zhinji mukati mangu Kunyaradza kwenyu kunofadza mweya wangu.
\v 20 Chigaro chezvakaipa chingashamwaridzana nemwi here, Icho chinofunga kuita zvakashata nemitemo yacho?
\v 21 Vanounganira upenyu hwowakarurama, Vachipa mhosva ropa risina mhosva.
\v 22 Asi Jehovha ndiye nhare yangu yakasimba; Mwari wangu idombo routiziro hwangu.
\v 23 Achadzosera pamusoro pavo kutadza kwavo, Achavaparadza pakati pokuita kwavo; Jehovha Mwari wedu achavaparadza.
